- It's true.

01:11:29.402 --> 01:11:32.574
- I want your cage cleared by 9:00!
- What did he say?

01:11:32.674 --> 01:11:34.578
- I'd like to make five points.
- In a moment.

01:11:34.678 --> 01:11:38.514
