to do it for us.

01:12:49.575 --> 01:12:52.658
Fifthly: May I remind you
it takes at least 18 months...

01:12:52.758 --> 01:12:54.961
to decommission a zoological
facility of this kind.

01:12:55.061 --> 01:12:57.663
- Shut up or I'll shoot!
- My God! He's gone mad.

01:12:57.763 --> 01:13:00.102
What's this, the latest
Harvard Business School technique?

01:13:00.202 --> 01:13:02.801
Or merely an extension
of your policy of consultation?

01:13:02.901 --> 01:13:04.672
- You would rather talk than live?
- You won't shoot me.

01:13:04.772 --> 01:13:07.374
- I will!
- Not with a 7.65 Baretta .34.

01:13:07.474 --> 01:13:11.057
- Oh, really? Why not?
- The safety catch is still on.

01:13:12.066 --> 01:13:14.534
Grab him!
Get the gun, get the gun!

01:13:15.971 --> 01:13:19.020
What in bloody hell's
going on here?

01:13:19.120 --> 01:13:21.991
Dad! You look great!
How ya doin'?

01:13:22.091 --> 01:13:24.068
Clear off, you freaks!

01:13:25.647 --> 01:13:27.614
- Who in bloody hell are you?
- This is Rollo Lee.

01:13:29.017 --> 01:13:32.201
Mr. McCain. I'd like to make
five points about the zoo.

01:13:32.301 --> 01:13:34.255
- Go away.
- Point one: The zoo...

01:13:37.326 --> 01:13:42.112
- You've been stealing from me again.
- Stealing?

01:13:42.212 --> 01:13:45.950
- My God, I've caught you red-handed.
- Oh, that!

01:13:46.050 --> 01:13:47.717
I was just putting that back.
I borrowed that...

01:13:47.817 --> 01:13:50.554
- Neville's gone to the police.
- What?

01:13:50.654 --> 01:13:55.894
- You're going to jail, Vince.
- Oh, no! Not again!

01:13:55.994 --> 01:13:58.995
Mr. McCain, Vince'll put the money back.
I promise.

01:13:59.095 --> 01:14:02.532
Sorry, Willa, but I'm gonna
have to close the zoo too.

01:14:02.632 --> 01:14:06.068
What? Why? We're up to 20%!

01:14:06.168 --> 01:14:09.442
- No, you're not.
- Oh, we are! We are with this!

01:14:09.542 --> 01:14:11.743
- Are you sure?
- I swear it.

01:14:11.843 --> 01:14:13.127
Nearly 25.

01:14:15.334 --> 01:14:18.516
All right, I'll leave it open.
But don't let it drop.

01:14:18.616 --> 01:14:20.594
