or I'll kill you.

01:14:25.010 --> 01:14:28.395
- You won't shoot me.
- Oh, yes, I will.

01:14:28.495 --> 01:14:31.434
You haven't got the guts
to shoot your own father.

01:14:31.534 --> 01:14:34.646
Yes, I do! Get back!

01:14:36.255 --> 01:14:38.121
Go on then.

01:14:39.359 --> 01:14:41.941
Go on, you spineless twat!

01:14:42.041 --> 01:14:45.781
See?
You're no son of mine.

01:14:45.881 --> 01:14:48.251
Oh, yeah, good idea!

01:14:48.351 --> 01:14:51.120
Give us all a good laugh,
